OL,3,CTeen, 19, sentenced for causing the
OL,4,Cdeaths of three teenagers in crash
OL,6,FThe mother of Tilly Seccombe whose
OL,7,Fdaughter was killed in the crash has
OL,8,Fspoken to ITV News Central in the wake
OL,9,Fof the sentencing, as Pablo Taylor
OL,10,Freports.
OL,12,FA teenage motorist who admitted
OL,13,Fcausing the deaths of three passengers
OL,14,Fin a two-car crash five weeks after he
OL,15,Fpassed his driving test has been
OL,16,Fsentenced.
OL,18,FEdward Spencer lost control of the car
OL,19,Fbetween Chipping Campden and Shipston-
OL,20,Fon-Stour whilst on his way home from
OL,21,Fschool in April 2023.
