OL,3,CTeen, 19, sentenced for causing the
OL,4,Cdeaths of three teenagers in crash
OL,6,FHe has been banned from driving for
OL,7,Feight years and has been sentenced to
OL,8,Ftwo years in a young offenders
OL,9,Finstitution.
OL,11,FHis passengers, Harry Purcell, 17,
OL,12,FMatilda "Tilly" Seccombe, 16, and
OL,13,FFrank Wormald, 16, all died in the
OL,14,Fcrash.
OL,16,FA woman and two children were also
OL,17,Fseriously injured in the crash after
OL,18,Fthe car Spencer was driving crashed
OL,19,Fhead on into them. They were left with
OL,20,Flife-changing injuries.
