OL,3,CTeen, 19, sentenced for causing the
OL,4,Cdeaths of three teenagers in crash
OL,6,FSpencer, from Newbold on Stour,
OL,7,Fpreviously pleaded guilty at Warwick
OL,8,FCrown Court to causing death by
OL,9,Fcareless driving and three counts of
OL,10,Fcausing serious injury by careless or
OL,11,Finconsiderate driving.
OL,13,FHe has been banned from driving for
OL,14,Feight years and has been sentenced to
OL,15,Ftwo years in a young offenders
OL,16,Finstitution.
OL,18,FWarwickshire Police said the case
OL,19,Fshowed the "devastating consequences"
OL,20,Fof a car being driven carelessly.
