OL,6,FJudge Andrew Lockhart KC was told
OL,7,FSpencer, of Armscote Road, Newbold-on-
OL,8,FStour, Warwickshire, only passed his
OL,9,Fdriving test six weeks earlier but
OL,10,Fsocial media videos discovered after
OL,11,Fthe crash had exposed a history of
OL,12,F"showing off, driving too quickly and
OL,13,Ffailing to heed the warnings of those
OL,14,Fwho were in the car with him".
OL,16,FIt also emerged that Tilly had
OL,17,Fpreviously sent a Snapchat message to
OL,18,FSpencer complaining about his driving
OL,19,Fbut he had responded that she had
OL,20,F"underestimated" him.
